lian recipe. Ricotta salata is a slightly aged version of ricotta. Ricotta <i>al forno<\/i> is a brick of dense, solidified (pressed) ricotta coated with salt. This effect is achieved by slowly baking and sometimes smoking the pressed ricotta.","You can replace the bow tie pasta with spaghetti, ribbons etc.","You can replace ricotta salata with regular ricotta.","You can replace ricotta with grated Manchego cheese."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","50m","6 portion"]}